room_title: Escape room "The Deadly Dining Room" by Crazy Cat Escape Room in Houston
room_description: As his last wish, your eccentric uncle Chad Chadley has invited you to a special will-reading party. As you gather in the dining room of his mansion, the tension is high: who will inherit the fortune? Suddenly the doors lock in, and as the final surprise, your uncle has left clues and puzzles to try to escape this Deadly Dining Room.
